Subject: Re: [T2] Anti-Seize and spark plugs

I think seized spark plugs are a consequence of people who think they
are fire-and-forget ammunition. I would think that people who remove
them regularly to check cleanliness and gap at regular tune-up
intervals are unlikely to encounter seized threads.

